ral steps ahead during each battle, plotting the optimal use of each character’s action points.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426900/extras/4ce131c16c2252e19db5fa7948c90cdd.avif?t=1727785505\" width=600 height=224 /></span><br><br><strong>Your weapons, bandages, and other items deteriorate</strong>, and your resources are very limited. Make sure your companions rest, or panic may overtake them.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Oh… And expect to die. A lot.</h2>",
